From: Meng Yi <meng.yi@nxp.com>
Date: Mon, 28 Dec 2015 17:37:58 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0249/1429] arm: dts: ls1021a-twr: add SII9022A HDMI DT node

Signed-off-by: Xiubo Li <Li.Xiubo@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Yi <meng.yi@nxp.com>
[Original patch taken from QorIQ-SDK-V2.0-20160527-yocto]
Signed-off-by: Yanjiang Jin <yanjiang.jin@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-twr.dts |    6 ++++++
 1 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-twr.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-twr.dts
index a1c62f7..9450528 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-twr.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-twr.dts
@@ -182,6 +182,12 @@
 		VDDIO-supply = <&reg_3p3v>;
 		clocks = <&sys_mclk 1>;
 	};
+
+	hdmi: sii9022a@39 {
+	      compatible = "fsl,sii902x";
+	      reg = <0x39>;
+	      interrupts = <GIC_SPI 167 IRQ_TYPE_EDGE_RISING>;
+	};
 };
 
